#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga "
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Arahantasutta "
msgstr "24. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.434, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.24:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.24:1.2"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhiṃsu, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhiṃsu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, whatever perfected ones, fully awakened Buddhas truly wake up—in the past, "

#. VAR: hi → yepi hi (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.24:1.3"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhissanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhissanti. "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.24:1.4"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhanti. "
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.24:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.3"
msgid "Ye hi, keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhiṃsu … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever perfected ones, fully awakened Buddhas truly wake up—in the past, "

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.4"
msgid "abhisambujjhissanti … "
msgstr "future, "

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.5"
msgid "abhisambujjhanti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhanti. "
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.24:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.24:3.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
